ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS in order to add the CZECH REPUBLIC to the list of countries and territories whose citizens are exempt from the temporary resident visa requirement for travel to Canada.
